window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>As Mason strengthens his magic over metal and stone, the Master lurks in the shadows. </p> <p>To lure the Master out and stop his nefarious plot, Mason and his harem of mages and princesses have to do several things: </p> <ol> <li>Take over the Order of Mages </li> <li>Build a train and railroad system to connect the kingdoms of Illaria and Cedis </li> <li>Keep from getting burned by giant, murderous creatures made of flame </li> </ol> <p>Sounds like a piece of cake, right?</p>"; 
